data.value: Fulfilling a need of his people,Mr.Anuradha, the former director of multisports club decided to start this huge project of establishing a sports club in his home town, Mawathagama. At the begining, in 2006, only a gym and a swimming pool was there with 50 registered members. But after 12 successful years , now we have a gym with newest technology, 2 swimming pools, 2 tennis courts, 2 indoor badminton courts and a billiard room with all the facilities. In the present we have more than 100 registered members and some of them had won national and international tournaments in tennis, badminton and swimming. And also we have all the facilities to deal with more than 20 daily customers. This is the place where you can get the best facilities for a less cost. So come and join with us!
